## 3. How to Build

Both services use Maven. To build:

Run commands from each service directory.

---

## 4. How to Run the Services

### **UserManagementService**

Default port: **8080**

### **TweetService**

Default port: **8082**

---

## 5. API Testing Instructions

### 1) Register User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/register

### 2) Login User (returns token)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/login

### 3) Create Tweet
POST http://localhost:8082/tweets  
Headers:


### 4) Get All Producers
GET http://localhost:8082/producers

### 5) Get Messages by Producer
GET http://localhost:8082/messages/producer/{id}

### 6) Get Messages Visible to Subscriber
GET http://localhost:8082/messages/subscriber/{id}

